Use of Parks Near Waterbodies

01-01-2020 to 01-31-2020, Roanoke City, VA
Notes:
This map shows user activities in parks/greenways near waterbodies in Roanoke City, VA. A five (5) meters buffer was created around targeted parks to calibrate GPS horizontal accuracy. You may change the layer visability on the top-right corner.

Base map attributes to mapbox API.
